&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;doc-tabs&quot;&gt;Tabs&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Split your content into tabs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;textarea&gt;
[tabs-container]
[tab title=&quot;First tab&quot;]Tab content here[/tab]
[tab title=&quot;Second tab&quot;]Tab content here[/tab]
[tab title=&quot;Third tab&quot;]Tab content here[/tab]
[/tabs-container]
&lt;/textarea&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;doc-lists&quot;&gt;Lists&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This shortcode allows you to create styled lists. It supports the &quot;class&quot; attribute which is optional.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;textarea&gt;
[ul class=&quot;square&quot;]
[li]First li element[/li]
[li]Second li element[/li]
[li]etc.[/li]
[/ul]
&lt;/textarea&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h3 id=&quot;doc-button&quot;&gt;Button&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This shortcode allows you to display a button. The &quot;featured&quot; attribute will display a bigger and centered button - include featured buttons preferably only in narrow areas to avoid full-width buttons.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;textarea&gt;
[button url=&quot;#&quot;]Scroll back to top[/button]
[button featured=1 url=&quot;http://www.example.com/buy_now.html&quot;]Buy Now[/button]
[button url=&quot;#contact&quot;]Scroll to contact form[/button]
&lt;/textarea&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h3 id=&quot;doc-separator&quot;&gt;Separator&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This shortcode allows you to include a line wherever you want to make a separation. It supports an optional &quot;class&quot; attribute.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Examples:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;textarea&gt;
[separator]
[separator class=&quot;between-rows&quot;]
[separator class=&quot;add-top&quot;]
[separator class=&quot;add-bottom&quot;]
[separator class=&quot;add-top add-bottom&quot;]
&lt;/textarea&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;doc-widgets&quot;&gt;Widgets&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This shortcode allows you to display a widgets area. There are 10 areas available that you can fill with any widget you want in the Widgets page. The &quot;area&quot; attribute is required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Examples:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;textarea&gt;
[widgets area=one]
[widgets area=two]
[widgets area=ten]
&lt;/textarea&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;doc-easy-columns&quot;&gt;Easy Columns&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;These shortcodes are required to set the layout of your pages/posts. Place one or more columns into a row, you can add as many rows as you want to have different layouts on the page.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;No-sidebar example:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;textarea&gt;
[row]
[fullwidth-column]Your content[/fullwidth-column]
[/row]
&lt;/textarea&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Left-sidebar example:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;textarea&gt;
[row]
[one-third-column]...Left-sidebar content...[/one-third-column]
[two-thirds-column]...Main content here...[/two-thirds-column]
[/row]
&lt;/textarea&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Right-sidebar example:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;textarea&gt;
[row]
[two-thirds-column]...Main content here...[/two-thirds-column]
[one-third-column]...Right-sidebar content...[/one-third-column]
[/row]
&lt;/textarea&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Three columns example:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;textarea&gt;
[row]
[one-third-column]...Feature 1...[/one-third-column]
[one-third-column]...Feature 2...[/one-third-column]
[one-third-column]...Feature 3...[/one-third-column]
[/row]
&lt;/textarea&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Optional attribute&lt;/strong&gt;: &quot;class&quot; – &lt;em&gt;allows you to add a CSS class to a column, example: [one-third-column class=&quot;box&quot;]&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note&lt;/strong&gt;: always surround your content with columns. If you don&#039;t want a sidebar then use the &quot;no-sidebar&quot; shortcode – &lt;em&gt;this is required in order to keep margin consistency for layouts with and without sidebars&lt;/em&gt;.

&lt;h3 id=&quot;doc-advanced-columns&quot;&gt;Advanced Columns&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you want even more flexibility and are not satisfied with the above column possibilities, then this shortcode provides you full control over the width of each area/column.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Important&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;: The width of the layout is &quot;sixteen columns&quot; therefor you need to complete a total of sixteen columns for each row.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example of a 4 columns layout (16/4 = four):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;textarea&gt;
[row]
[column width=four]First section[/column]
[column width=four]Second section[/column]
[column width=four]Third section[/column]
[column width=four]Fourth section[/column]
[row]&lt;/textarea&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example of how the welcome block (note the &quot;box dark&quot; CSS classes) is made (seven + nine = 16) :&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;textarea&gt;
[row class=&quot;box dark&quot;]
[column width=seven]Welcome text![/column]
[column width=nine]Images slider goes here[/column]
[row]
&lt;/textarea&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note:&lt;/strong&gt; The &quot;width&quot; attribute is required and must be filled with a word number in English from &quot;one&quot; (very small width) to &quot;sixteen&quot; (full width).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;doc-main-slider&quot;&gt;Landing-page Slider&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This shortcode allows you to display the main images slider bumbled with welcoming text. Images and texts are configurable in the &quot;Landing-page Slider&quot; tab on the left of this page.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;textarea&gt;
[welcome-block]
&lt;/textarea&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;doc-contact-form&quot;&gt;Contact Form&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This shortcode allows you to include the contact form. Go to the &quot;Contact form&quot; tab on the left of this page in order to set your email address.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;textarea&gt;
[contact-form]
&lt;/textarea&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;doc-video&quot;&gt;Video&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This shortcode allows you to embed any external videos with responsive support (it will scale with the layout and keep correct video ratio).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;textarea&gt;
[video]&lt;iframe src=&quot;http://www.youtube.com/embed/k9cAyb_Iqow&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;[/video]
&lt;/textarea&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example of an embedded video within a column:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;textarea class=&quot;bigger&quot;&gt;
[row]
[half-column]
Video description goes here
[/half-column]

[half-column]
[video]&lt;iframe src=&quot;http://www.youtube.com/embed/k9cAyb_Iqow&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;[/video]
[/half-column]
[/row]
&lt;/textarea&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;doc-content-sliders&quot;&gt;Content Sliders&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Slide anything, from images, videos or simple text. You can display as many sliders as you want at the same time and with different options for each as you require.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Simple example:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;textarea&gt;
[slides-container]
[slide]Your content here...[/slide]
[slide]Another here...[/slide]
[/slides-container]
&lt;/textarea&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can control all options of each slider using the following attributes:&lt;br /&gt;
animation=&quot;fade&quot; (&quot;slide&quot; or &quot;fade&quot;)&lt;br /&gt;
animation_speed=&quot;fast&quot; (&quot;slow&quot; or &quot;fast&quot;)&lt;br /&gt;
delay_between_slides=&quot;short&quot; (&quot;short&quot; or &quot;long&quot;)&lt;br /&gt;
hide_controls=1 (if you don&#039;t want the navigation buttons)
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example with fast animation but long delay between slides:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;textarea&gt;
[slides-container animation_speed=&quot;fast&quot; delay_between_slides=&quot;long&quot;]
[slide]Your content here...[/slide]
[slide]Another here...[/slide]
[/slides-container]
&lt;/textarea&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
